name: We Love Dogs
description: We Love Dogs ($DOGS) is the ultimate community-driven token for dog lovers across the globe. Built on Ethereum, $DOGS celebrates the timeless bond between humans and man’s best friend through memes, culture, and an ever-growing pack of holders. With an active community, fun branding, and a mission to bring people together, $DOGS goes beyond being just another memecoin — it’s a social movement. Whether through shared laughter, future community initiatives, or upcoming utilities like merch and governance, We Love Dogs embodies wag energy that’s here to stay.
